  <brief_title>Value of CT-based Autopsy Compared With Conventional Autopsy in ICU Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Computertomography-based Autopsy (Virtopsy) Versus Conventional Autopsy in Patients Dying in Intensive Care Units</official_title>
  <sponsors>
